data.description: Welcome to 14007 Teaneck Terrace, a stunning retreat in the sought-after community of North Potomac. This meticulously maintained home offers a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living. Don't miss out on a rare chance to secure your spot in the highly rated and coveted Wootton High School district. Step inside to find a generous floor plan with ample living space. The sunlit living and dining rooms are ideal for comfortable living and entertaining. The heart of the home, the kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. Cooking and hosting will be a joy in this beautiful space.  The luxurious master suite offers a spacious bedroom, lots of closet space, and a bathroom with an upgraded shower.  Private Backyard: Step outside to the private fenced in backyard oasis with a spacious patio, perfect for outdoor dining and entertaining. The lush landscaping provides a serene and relaxing atmosphere.  This home is quietly tucked away in a nice peaceful neighborhood, but still conveniently located. It is just 3.6 miles to Shady Grove hospital and Fallsgrove shopping center with tons of restaurants and stores including Starbucks, Chipotle, Panera, Smoothie King, Capital One, and more. 3 miles to Travilah Square shopping center with Trader Joe's, 7-Eleven, Sunoco Gas station, and more. This rare opportunity is now back on the market, but likely not for long
